CustomField.description: Indicator as to whether the duplicate was lead, contact or account.
CustomField.formula: IF( AND( NOT( ISNULL( SFSSDupeCatcher__Account__c ) ), SFSSDupeCatcher__Account__c <> '' ), 'Account', IF( AND( NOT( ISNULL( SFSSDupeCatcher__Contact__c ) ), SFSSDupeCatcher__Contact__c <> '' ), 'Contact', IF( AND( NOT( ISNULL( SFSSDupeCatcher__Lead__c ) ), SFSSDupeCatcher__Lead__c <> '' ), 'Lead', '' ) ) )
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Indicator as to whether the duplicate is a lead, contact or account.
CustomField.label: Duplicate Type
